  "voice": "The MEATS presents itself as an artisanal meat experience that transcends ordinary dining. The brand voice balances sophistication with approachability, treating meat preparation as both science and art. Language focuses on craftsmanship, heritage, and the sensory experience of quality meat. Conversational but elevated, with subtle humor about meat culture woven throughout. Avoids foodie clich\u00e9s, instead emphasizing authenticity and intentional detail. Every interaction reinforces the premium, exclusive nature of the experience.",
